{
  "id": "tier5_indus_readings",
  "name": "Tier 5 — Indus Script Structural Readings Analysis",
  "description": "Deep structural analysis of the Indus Script corpus for reading-pattern research. Computes positional profiles (I/M/T rates), symbol clustering, bigram frequencies, Zipf distribution, entropy, and writing-system classification. Produces the sign-level data needed to identify logograms, determinatives, and phonogram candidates. All results are merged and exported for downstream research.",
